INSERT INTO `wp_options` VALUES('1006', 'wpb_js_templates', 'a:1:{s:16:\"module_679802204\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"module\";s:8:\"template\";s:5670:\"[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"1628\" img_size=\"medium\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]\n<h4 style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Short Description</h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">DynamicHRIS Travel and Expense Management Solution caters to streamline and automate the submission and approval of multiple expenses and expense types. Expenses include travel, lodging, car rentals, meals, etc. It focuses on restructuring your company\'s present travel expense management system to cut losses and maximize profits. DynamicHRIS is an integrated travel and expense solution, which helps organizations save time and money spend during every step of the business journey before, during, and after the trip. Built-in workflow and travel rules allow managers to quickly and easily approve expenses.</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"FEATURES\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][stm_color_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1654\" css_animation=\"appear\" css=\".vc_custom_1441005324395{margin-top: 12px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"border_right\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Simplify business travel &amp; expenses.</strong></h4>\nBook business travel from a broad selection of in-policy options. Travel Booking can be routed to HOD / Reportee for Approval.\n<h4></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/12\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/12\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1659\" css_animation=\"appear\" css=\".vc_custom_1441005343808{margin-top: 12px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"border_right\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Make business travel and expense management simple.</strong></h4>\nEmployees can manage domestic and international travel, reserve rental cars and make hotel and rail reservations - all from a single system.\n<h4></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1682\" css_animation=\"appear\" css=\".vc_custom_1441089370438{margin-top: 12px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"border_right\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Put an end to manual labor.</strong></h4>\nNo one wants to key in the same data, multiple times in multiple systems. With travel and expense management solution, manual, paper-based expense reports are a thing of the past. Admin and Accounts team can easily review, approve, process, audit and pay expense reports. Organizations can better improve control and gain visibility into travel and entertainment (T&amp;E) spending.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/12\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/12\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1685\" css_animation=\"appear\" css=\".vc_custom_1441005834241{margin-top: 12px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"border_right\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Stay one step ahead.</strong></h4>\nTravel and expense is not a static process. The industry constantly changes. With the right tools, you\'ll be able to adapt and adjust your processes and your policies to meet new business and regulatory requirements. Our T&amp;E module also adapts to individual traveler preferences for organizations large and small. From pre-trip approval to reimbursement to all the steps in between, T&amp;E can help.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1684\" css_animation=\"appear\" css=\".vc_custom_1441089402292{margin-top: 12px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"border_right\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Improve planning with trip organization.</strong></h4>\nAfter you book your business travel, managing all the trip details - from air, hotel, dining reservations and more - can be time consuming and disorganized. With T&amp;E‘s integration, all of your trip information is organized and accessible in one place.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/12\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/12\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"1683\" css_animation=\"appear\" css=\".vc_custom_1441089478149{margin-top: 12px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"border_right\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Centralized Policy Management</strong></h4>\nManage all rules and policies from central location, policies can set as per your grade, designation, Level, band etc. Policies can be set for all expenses viz. travel, lodging, food, telephone, internet etc.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"SCREENSHOTS\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][stm_color_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_images_carousel images=\"1720,1721,1722,1723,1724,1725,1726,1727,1730,1729,1728\" img_size=\"full\" slides_per_view=\"6\" autoplay=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}}', 'no');
